In [76]:
markers = ['o', '*', '.', ',', 'x', 'X', '+', 'P', 's', 'D', 'd', 'p', 
           'H', 'h', 'v', '^', '<', '>', '1', '2', '3', '4', '|', '_']

for m in markers:
    print(m)
    plt.plot(df['Year'], df['GDP_Growth'], m)
    plt.xlabel('Year')
    plt.ylabel('GDP GRowth')
    plt.title('Economy of US')
    plt.show()

Change line style¶

In [77]:
line = ['-',':','--','-.']
for l in line:
    print(l)
    l = 'o' + l + 'r'
    plt.plot(df['Year'], df['GDP_Growth'], l)
    plt.xlabel('Year')
    plt.ylabel('GDP GRowth')
    plt.title('Economy of US')
    plt.show()

Add legend¶

In [108]:

plt.plot(df['Year'], df['Inflation'], label = 'Inflation' )
plt.plot(df['Year'], df['Unemployment'], label = 'Unemployment')
plt.xlabel('Year')
plt.ylabel('Economy')
plt.grid()
plt.legend()
